---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy — Mapache Softworks"
	description="Privacy policy for Mapache Softworks and its apps and services."
>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container legal">
			<p class="eyebrow">Data protection</p>
			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="lede">This is a launch draft. Review and update it with a qualified legal advisor before publishing mapache-soft.com.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<div class="container legal panel">
			<h2>Who is responsible</h2>
			<p>The data controller for this website and the services offered here is:</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Mapache Softworks</strong><br />
				[Street address], [Postal code] [City], Austria<br />
				Email: <a href="mailto:hello@mapache-soft.com">hello@mapache-soft.com</a>
			</p>

			<h2>What data we collect and why</h2>
			<p>We only collect and process personal data when there is a specific purpose and a valid legal basis for doing so.</p>
			<ul class="list">
				<li><strong>Contact emails:</strong> When you email us, we process your address and message content to respond and correspond with you.</li>
				<li><strong>Website visits:</strong> This static site does not use analytics cookies or trackers by default. Hosting infrastructure may log technical data such as IP address, browser type, and requested pages for security and availability.</li>
				<li><strong>App usage:</strong> Our apps process files locally on your device by default and do not send file contents or filenames to our servers unless a feature explicitly requires it.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Legal basis</h2>
			<p>Processing is based on your consent, contract performance, legal obligations, or our legitimate interest to operate the website and communicate with visitors, depending on the specific situation.</p>

			<h2>How long we keep data</h2>
			<p>We retain personal data only as long as necessary for the purpose it was collected, or as required by law.</p>

			<h2>Your rights</h2>
			<p>Under the GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, erase, restrict processing, object to processing, and request data portability. You can contact us at any time to exercise these rights.</p>

			<h2>Third-party services</h2>
			<p>We may link to external websites or use hosting and communication providers. Those providers process data under their own privacy policies.</p>

			<h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
			<p>We may update this policy as the website, apps, or legal requirements change. The current version is always available on this page.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.legal.panel .list {
		margin-top: 24px;
	}
</style>
